summary_to_eng: Copy and Paste from local computer
Text_Summa: Copy and Paste from local computer When copying files from local computers clipboard stores only filepath on a drive and pasting on Canvas would do nothing. Because we don't have actual file in clipboard and don't know its type. To do it we need to implement some kind of Parser which would understand clipboard data and if it's filepath try to load it with File API and put in on canvas

summary_to_eng: Wrong link "go to classes" on the student invite page
Text_Summa: Wrong link "go to classes" on the student invite page # Open [https://student-staging.teacherly.io/password/reset|https://student-staging.teacherly.io/password/reset][~accountid:5b67bcd8e6dba529eefda937] Here is the old student logic. We need to decide what to do here. Probably; if the user is already authenticated and clicks on the invitation link again; then he should be redirected to the student room without any “go to classes”. And if someone tries to request a url with a non-existent token; then I would throw a 403 or redirect to the login page; not the wrong token.[~accountid:5cee2d23919eaf0f2135ac64] don't fully understand the problem. Can we sync for 10 minutes?Agreed to do the next check. If the user is not authorized and the reset token is valid; then we log in and redirect to the student immediately. If the user is not authorized and the token does not exist; then we redirect to the root page with logins. If the user is authorized; then to the student.After the student has passed the activation of the invite; he is redirected to the student dashboard. Since we cannot login a user from one dashboard to another; the student gets to the login form.Checked fix. Now the user redirects on the main page and doesn't confuse when he/she saw Invalid token message previously.

summary_to_eng: Zero Date, Datetime, and Timestamp values
Text_Summa: Zero Date, Datetime, and Timestamp values Found in laravel docs. Starting with MySQL 5.7; {{0000-00-00 00:00:00}} is no longer considered a valid date. As documented at the [+Laravel 5.2 upgrade guide+|https://laravel.com/docs/5.2/upgrade#upgrade-5.2.0]; all timestamp columns should receive a valid default value when you insert records into your database. You may use the {{useCurrent()}} column modifier (from Laravel 5.1.25 and above) in your migrations to default the timestamp columns to the current timestamps; or you may make the timestamps {{nullable()}} to allow null values.

summary_to_eng: Add coloring of linked user cards
Text_Summa: Add coloring of linked user cards [~takt911] Coloring the linked map is done in such a way; in the appendix there is a list with a color palette of 10 gradients; we sum the last 4 digits of the map and take the remainder of the division by 10; as a result we get a number from 0 to 9; which we substitute into our list with palettes and pull out the gradient. Thus; on different phones under the same account in the application; the same card will be painted with the same color; but unfortunately there may be duplicate colors; but I think that is rare. Do you like this logic of card coloring?[~pavel] Ok; I'll have to test it; users usually don't have many cards; but even then there is a risk that; for example; only 2 cards are tied up and both will be in the same colorcards are displayed in the color that is attached to them. all OK

MIC-301 Social login networks Authorization through Google cannot be done simply through allauth. The user will have to redirect to apihi and the api will have to record the session. You should not do this; because in this case; for some users we will have authorization by tokens without sessions; and for others without tokens; but with sessions. You will need to dig into the doc: [https://developers.google.com/identity/protocols/OAuth2WebServer] and integrate it into our token authorization process. Unfortunately there is no obvious documentation in the rest-auth docThen I searched / studied different packages for authorization by social networks. networks; trying to apply a solution that authorized only by tokens; avoiding sessions. I even started to implement an authorization service that absolutely does not save state and does not use sessions; having previously tried to find similar solutions on the Internet - I did not find it. As a result; I quit this case; because I came to the conclusion that the solution is absolutely pointless and I did not find a similar solution in Google for this very reason.

API - Web Create account [~alexander.medvedev] is waiting for [~vasily.toropchin] update on doc he needAdd validation for sign-up fieldsAdd password validation for at least 6 charactersFrom SamatCustomer: [https://gitlab.com/sortedhouse/backend/blob/develop/docs/api.md#sign-up-1]https://pm.maddevs.co/browse/SOR-29?focusedCommentId=65781&page=com.atlassian.jira.plugin.system.issuetabpanels%3Acomment-tabpanel#comment-65781https://pm.maddevs.co/browse/SOR-29?focusedCommentId=66427&page=com.atlassian.jira.plugin.system.issuetabpanels%3Acomment-tabpanel#comment-66427The reason i reopened the ticket is to review one issue related to _*Terms and Condition acceptance*_. By the business requirements _Terms and Condition_ should be accepted by a user; so as we have the Terms and Condition acceptance step is the last and there could a case when the sign-up process could be terminated by accident. But on the previous steps all filled in data are saved; so further a user without acceptance can already sign-in and use the services at all.[~kairat] the simplest way to solve it is adding one more attribute to a response after sign-in. It would be a boolean attribute; which described have users accept the terms or not. Then the frontend can add a message to users about this state. And disable functions if it's needed.another issue is there is no endpoint of customers to specify which kind of notification to receive - email; sms or both.in docs i cant find the way to specify to accept terms by a customer. if there is the way; so which endpoint is that?sign in endpoint is broken now; it is returning 404for customer there is no way to save addressthere is an issue of signup endpoint; the password field is throwing error - password must be 6 chars even if send "Hello2012".[~kairat] and [~samat.jukeshov] here is the documents for Customer Registration End Points:when trying to sign up with data:customer signup* Updated documentation for Customer Sign up [https://gitlab.com/sortedhouse/backend/blob/feature/SOR-30/docs/api.md#sign-up]

summary_to_eng: Adding Google Maps to Customer account with marker
Text_Summa: Adding Google Maps to Customer account with marker [~vasily.toropchin] could you please pinpoint to place where frontend developer should get Customer Location for a job exactly?[~samat.jukeshov]; so the concept here is that Job has it is own location. So the Job object with have the location related object in it. And there is information regarding the job's location.I think that guys could use either Postcode itself; or more likely they will user coordinates in locations with X and Y in it. Where X is latitude and Y is longitude.[~samat.jukeshov] probably; we should add some info for location in the Admin panel; like coordinates; county and town. Text_Summa: Set up Google Analytics Enhanced Ecommerce with GTM and IT for ALL TRANSACTIONS As we discuss today; this task will start from 21 Feb2020; and finish on 24 Feb2020[ ~huongbn@topica.edu.vn ] this task may take time. a lot of things to do.[ ~ducnh2@topica.edu.vn ] Today let me know your estimated time for finishing this task; okay?We need to set up GA Enhanced Ecommerce for 2 parts of products:[~hungcm] [~tuanlq] pls help us on this task.[ ~ducnh2@topica.edu.vn ]: discuss with [~tuanlq] or [~hungcm] to estimate deadline for this task today[ ~leonov.rs@gmail.com ] we setup EEC on our webiste; now you can view some ecommerce reports in Google Analytic; please check at 'Only Edumall.vn' viewGive me details please:this task seems much more complicated than expected. Someone set up EEC for edumall.vn about 1 year ago but it seems not set up correctly and the data is very different from what we have in our database.How do you think how much time do you need?These are the following steps that we will take to fully integrate enhanced eCommerce:[ ~anhdn16@topica.edu.vn ] any sub-tasks on that?[ ~anhdn16@topica.edu.vn ] hi; create subtasks please for each of these steps. It would be better to track this task.[~hungcm] [~hoangld2] we need IT helps to finish this task. pls take time to discuss with us.[~tuanlq] pay your attention please. We have discussed this task with you today.[~hoangld2] em check cái này nhé. bị miss lấu quá rồi.[~hoangld2] task nay la highest priority. ấp dung JOc.30 (4-12-24) triệt để nhé.[ ~anhdn16@topica.edu.vn ] follow kĩ task này điHey all. Sorry for lately updating work notes. After talking to [ ~anhdn16@topica.edu.vn ] and [ ~ducnh2@topica.edu.vn ]. We have decided to low this task priority down to focus on https://jira.topica.vn/browse/WEWORK-66.[~hoangld2] hoàn thành sub-task thứ 1 trước nhé ạ; em đã set lại priority cho các sub-task rồi[ ~anhdn16@topica.edu.vn ] Subtask 1 hiện đang bị trùng với 1 subtask của https://jira.topica.vn/browse/WEWORK-66. Mình chuyển subtask đó qua bên kia nhé ?[~luandv] task cài EEC hiện đang ở đây; nếu chuyển được luồng thanh toán của LP về trên edumall thì anh ưu tiên thực hiện task đó trước nhé ạ; sau khi hoàn thành xong quay lại hoàn thiện EEC sautask này frozen thì change priority xuống low or lowest giúp a nhé; để highest; cứ lo lo [ ~ducnh2@topica.edu.vn ] [~hoangld2] [~khanhnn]Trang thanh toán online thành công đã hoàn thiện; vậy giờ đã có thể tiếp tục task này chưa ạ [~hoangld2][ ~anhdn16@topica.edu.vn ] okie nhé; bh anh lam[~hoangld2] có update gì task này ko em? 4 ngày mà ko thấy thay đổi trạng thái nhỉ[~hoangld2]Im doing it's subtask https://jira.topica.vn/browse/EVAB-80OK [~hoangld2] I got itI just re-opened all the sub-tasks besides https://jira.topica.vn/browse/EVAB-92 ([~Yann]; please confirm that EVAB-92 is done) so we can investigate what isn't done here.The current problems list:Also the issue:Important note - we need to create the testing GA and test everything there before pushing the data to production GA.No refunds and promo codes for ThailandWe will continue here: https://jira.topica.vn/browse/EVAB-269

Fix 5xx erros Daily track on Google webmaster toolhow many 5xx erros today? your estimated time to solve all of them? summary_to_eng: ĐẶT HÀNG FIX DATA XUẤT XUỐNG TỪ EROS
Text_Summa: ĐẶT HÀNG FIX DATA XUẤT XUỐNG TỪ EROS ok em để anh check lại case này nhé[~dungnv5] phần data xuất xuống bị lệch 7 tiếng so với thời gian hiển thị trên hệ thống. Check lại giúp t với nhé.[~dungnv5] comment phân tích và diễn giải vào đây cho anh sao cho định hướng được cho biz/it hiểu nhé. This action are being taken on the element with class equal to .lecture-preview. But its content can either have or not have the href attribute based on its asset_type field. Cannot reset my password [~ducla5] Researched reset password functionality. Checked it in staging and prod. There appears an error in both Prod and Staging. After clicking on "Forgot password?" link I was redirected to AccountKit page. Researched AccountKit service. I turns out that AccountKit is the Facebook's service for authentication without using passwords. AccountKit's workflow is as follow it uses emails and phone numbers where it sends codes; after which a user should enter that code and if the code is valid a user gets redirected back to their page where special callback handlers handle the data with user's token. If everything in that workflow is ok the page for changing password is opened and a user will be able to type new password.[~ducla5][~ducla5] we use gmail for sending letters but gmail restricts us to send 500 letter in a day. I consider we should choose mailing services such as SendGrid. Also I see some js files loading but they are the same.default bundling/merging/minification (+10 points on average)Regarding js optimizarion; I suggest to use builtin functionality. With this approach we will not rely on 3rd party solution; which is always good; since it does not increase overall system complexity - less possible bugs; less dev time wasted.[~denis.petrov] agreedTalking about the score; avg result will be between what we have with default setting(50); and with APO module(65). summary_to_eng: Meaning of COD Leads with Complete Status
Text_Summa: Meaning of COD Leads with Complete Status [~saran] [~Yann]There are two main type of lead (C3) shown in Minerva; c3_cod and c3_credit.Explored the code; looked for all pieces of code that could change e-payment status of c3_cod leads. Looked at Minerva and Marol. And found that such operations could be done in Marol; all other places doesn't seem to be related to it. Especially found update_payment_status method in app/controllers/contact_api_controller line 73. Third party services can change the type of the contactc3 by sending request to that action method passing the id and status of the contactc3 in parameters. If we send "complete" status for a contactc3 there will be a check for if there are other contactc3s with the same email; course_id; in case there are then all that contactc3s will have their statuses changed to "completed" and some of them may have type equal to c3_cod. That's what i managed to find[~azat17] Do we know what is the third party service that you mentioned?[~pornprapa] see the message above please[~saran] it's e-payment backend service; e-payment landing the ones i know so farIs it the same e-payment service that we are currently using?[~saran] Yes; it's the same we are using now. Also i'm not fully sure if other landings may or may not send this request to change the status.[~azat17] Any suggested solution to prevent this; I think it is not correct to have c3_cod with complete status in our database.[~saran] we can add a clause in that request by which not to take duplicated contactc3 which have c3_cod type . Such way i can prevent status updating of c3_cod leads in that request and further see if we get any c3_cod with complete status or not.[~azat17] Sounds good.[~saran] I will not affect other flow. It mustn't do thatAs I discussed with [~azat17]; I think this ticket is ready to deploy.

summary_to_eng: The system did not change the status of some leads from incomplete to timeout
Text_Summa: The system did not change the status of some leads from incomplete to timeout Normally; Lead type "c3_credit" has 4 main e-payment status. (Ideally; it should be like to logic below)Went through Minerva; Marol and e-payment applications. Didn't find any code; especially background jobs (crons) that would handle functionality of changing statuses. Found schedulers in e-payment java service and started to investigate it; it also has requests to Marol. But figured out that requests are for changing Ibanking status. Still need to look for this functionality[~Yann] FYI. A few updates.[~azat17] Please note that this issue occurs only a few percent. Most of the contacts status were changed correctly.Had a call with Saran. Regarding this task as i mentioned before the problem of updating statuses occurs because some Contactc3s have priority equal to 3. Found that js landing ([https://git.edumall.io/edumalltl/etl-epayment-gate]) sends a request to change priority to 3 when Omise returns failure response when a user does payments. I consider that some percent of contactc3 had an error returned from Omise. It can happen when the submitted data is incorrect or outdated (card number; cvv; expiration date) or when there isn't enough money on the cardThank you [~azat17].[~saran] sure; okay[~saran] Actually it was a research ticket. I spent the time investigating how does the system change statuses to timeout and found the reason why some leads have their statuses not changed to timeout due to priority being equal to 3. There is nothing to deploy here[~azat17] Could you give me a bit more detail?[~saran][~azat17] From your third answer (3); if the customer got 3 as their priority; why does it changed to failed?[~saran] You mean why despite having priority equal to 3 it doesn't change status to failed ? Correct me please if i'm wrong[~azat17] Correct.[~saran] let me research it

The user cannot login Invalid email or password.!99_1.png|thumbnail!I can successfully login/logout using my account.[~azat17] can you please take a look from an SSO side.I can reproduce this issue using prod db in local env.Issue related to quote items of this particular user. Since this user complains via phone that he can't login to his account on production; we can clean his quote manually through database as a quick solution.[~denis.petrov] [~kirill]From the code side; there are 2 magento core bugs here:

LMS issues - investigate and fix Here's our assumption at the moment.Checked all sidekiq workers whether they consume too much resources or not. Sidekiq was fine and we didn't notice huge memory consumption by it. We checked unicorn server and its configs. During the timeout we didn't see that unicorn consumes too much memory however it wasn't giving a response so afterwards we decided to increase the number of unicorn workers to 9 and reduced the request timeout speed from 600 sec to 30 sec. It helped now. If this issue happens again we're going to increase the number of unicorn workers and see how it affects the memory and plan our next stepsconfirm.[~ducla5] yeah; right. I hope we find the root. It couldn't have appeared from nothing because it used to be ok in previous weeks

Tracking button in payment page Checking the flow of COD and exploring how java e-payment service handles it.[~saran] [~pornprapa] I found that landing payment service after choosing COD sends requests toThank you [~azat17].[~saran] thanks. I think I'm going to handle it on my own. I found that an error appears before the request to the contactc3's status. I manage to fix that error then contacts' statuses should work corretlyDuring debugging the request of changing type of contactc3 i found that the request itself works fine. But for some landings there appears an error because ContactLDP becomes null. It happens sometimes during parsing price of courses. But the most funny part of this functionality was that if a user chooses COD payment and clicks on submit button they would always be redirected to cod-v5.html "thank you" page; no matter if the payment was successful or failure and users would think that everything is right. I now changed that logic in frontend and it shows error page with error messages[~azat17]Had a call with Saran where we discussed the current state of this ticket.The status was changed to c3_code correctly.You are welcome!
